The paper focuses on sampling algorithms for configurable software systems, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY) categories. The paper also discusses the use of algorithms in programming languages (cs.PL) and the importance of fault-detection in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
